{"tid":1187489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西伯利亞永凍土中發現獅子幼獸 距今3萬年前且呈冰凍狀態","createTime":"2019-06-05T16:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T17:02:17.000Z","uid":5338,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fab2dab7f5f33c0cdb04c392f91954cb3f65d9ab","tid":1187489,"uid":5338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://public.potaufeu.asahi.com/1c29-p/picture/16512772/767a99f2af34b4eac95d4e6edb9a15ab_640px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.potaufeu.asahi.com%2F1c29-p%2Fpicture%2F16512772%2F767a99f2af34b4eac95d4e6edb9a15ab_640px.jpg&h=24d93890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 俄羅斯與日本的聯合研究團隊於3日對外公布，已從西伯利亞的永凍土中，發現到呈冰凍狀態、過去生活於冰河時期的穴獅幼獸以及狼的頭部。據了解，兩者均為約3萬年前的個體，且處於能夠分辨出表情、「奇蹟般良好」的保存狀態。<br />\n<br />\n  根據研究團隊的公布內容指出，穴獅幼獸是於去年7月在西伯利亞東北部的河川附近發現。體長約40公分、體重800克左右，研判為剛出生不久。狼則是2～4歲，保留著牙齒及臉部的毛。兩者似乎均曾適應並生活在寒冷地區。<br />\n<br />\n  針對此2頭動物，曾運用X光電腦斷層掃描(CT)進行調查的東京慈惠會醫科大學客座教授‧鈴木直樹表示：「肌肉、內臟及腦部等皆被良好地保存下來。想要藉由跟現在的獅子與狼相比，查明當時的運動能力及生態」。該團隊曾於2015年以及2017年，共計發現到3頭穴獅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asahichinese-f.com/technology/12427096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasahichinese-f.com%2Ftechnology%2F12427096&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElryOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=249e5119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asahichinese-f.com/technology/12427096</a>"},{"pid":"507dca1a9371ccdbdfe776cfbca951641f93a620","tid":1187489,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de55fb4188faada0baa62bb5210012379db70d1","tid":1187489,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"復制技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd829beb487afc7254adf73b32d3499dc92e4de0","tid":1187489,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80416ca2229369d7bbbd435b97744afd1e363e2","tid":1187489,"uid":141871,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"0de55fb4188faada0baa62bb5210012379db70d1","tid":1187489,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"復制技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"四個字入面有兩個字都係錯嫁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母</span>"}]}